      "span_text": "The possible binding affinity between celastrol and the three proteasome catalytic subunits was predicted using molecular operating environment (MOE) program from the Chemical Computing Group Inc. as described previously.  As there was no information about human proteasome 3-D structure in PDB database, the 3D structure of bovine proteasome (PDB ID: 1IRU) was used."
